Format: `[TIME] - [LEVEL] - [OrderManager] - [MESSAGE]`

```
[2026-03-05 14:30:00 UTC] - [INFO]    - [OrderManager] - SPREAD CHECK OK: EURUSDc spread=1.3pips (max=3.0pips)
[2026-03-05 14:30:00 UTC] - [INFO]    - [OrderManager] - Sending BUY order: entry=1.08512, SL=1.08432, TP=1.08672, lot=0.01 | attempt=1/3
[2026-03-05 14:30:01 UTC] - [WARNING] - [OrderManager] - REQUOTE on attempt 1: retcode=10004. Recalculating from new bid/ask...
[2026-03-05 14:30:01 UTC] - [INFO]    - [OrderManager] - Retry attempt 2: new entry=1.08514, SL=1.08434, TP=1.08674
[2026-03-05 14:30:02 UTC] - [INFO]    - [OrderManager] - ORDER FILLED: ticket=123456789, fill_price=1.08514, slippage=+0.2pips
[2026-03-05 14:30:02 UTC] - [INFO]    - [OrderManager] - Trade logged to data/trade_log.csv | signal_id=abc12345

# Failure case:
[2026-03-05 16:45:00 UTC] - [WARNING] - [OrderManager] - SPREAD_TOO_HIGH: spread=8.7pips > max=3.0pips. Order ABORTED. [signal_id=def67890]
[2026-03-05 16:45:00 UTC] - [ERROR]   - [OrderManager] - REQUOTE_MAX: failed after 3 attempts. Order ABORTED. [signal_id=xyz11111]
```

